  <brief_title>A Study on the Efficacy and Safety of Benzonatate Soft Capsules for Improving Adult Cough Symptoms</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicentric Randomized Double-blind Placebo-controlled Study on the Efficacy and Safety of Benzonatate Soft Capsules for Improving Adult Cough Symptoms</official_title>
  <sponsors>
